Discover the Best Latin Restaurant in NYC – Yuca Bar

Looking for bold Latin flavors, handcrafted cocktails, and an electrifying nightlife scene? Yuca Bar, located in the heart of the East Village, is the go-to spot for authentic Latin cuisine, vibrant brunches, and legendary weekend parties. From crispy yuca fries to spicy mango margaritas, every dish and drink is crafted with passion. Plus, don’t miss our Happy Hour until 8 PM and Latin parties every Friday & Saturday featuring Reggaeton, Salsa, Bachata, and Merengue!

Our Story

Roots of Flavor:

The Story of Yuca Bar

Our story at Yuca Bar is rooted in the vibrant flavors, rhythms, and traditions of Latin culture. Located in the heart of New York, Yuca Bar was created to bring a slice of Latin warmth and energy to our community. Inspired by diverse Latin American cuisines, our menu blends traditional recipes with modern flair, served in an atmosphere that’s lively, welcoming, and filled with passion. We believe in great food, crafted cocktails, and unforgettable experiences that bring people together. Join us at Yuca Bar – where every meal, drink, and celebration is a journey through the heart of Latin America.
